adjectives.description: infrahuman (comparative more infrahuman, superlative most infrahuman)

entries.meaning: Below the level of the human.
examples: By his hubristic defiance of time, Dorian wanders into an infrahuman realm where he is at the mercy of pitiless daemonic agents.

entries.meaning: (psychology) A creature that is not (yet) at the level of understanding of a human being, such as a presymbolic child or an animal.
